

In case you receive the below error messages when trying to run docker-compose: 


ERROR: for phpmyadmin  Cannot start service phpmyadmin: driver failed programming external connectivity on endpoint dockerphpmysql_phpmyadmin_1 (0bb153c37917fbbbcf038b1face8435f63929a06c1d8d90d74621af7eb3b1afa): Error starting userland proxy: listen tcp 0.0.0.0:8080: bind: address already in use

ERROR: for nginx  Cannot start service nginx: driver failed programming external connectivity on endpoint dockerphpmysql_nginx_1 (c264e5229cbb1467dd373c06991dd8ac2827a7e621f3712534801283f82a3eec): Error starting userland proxy: listen tcp 0.0.0.0:80: bind: address already in use


1) Check which services are running on the mentioned ports (in this case, ports 80 and 8080), and kill them:

# lsof -i :8080
COMMAND  PID   USER   FD   TYPE DEVICE SIZE/OFF NODE NAME
tnslsnr 1479 oracle   13u  IPv6  27537      0t0  TCP *:http-alt (LISTEN)
# kill -9 1479
# lsof -i :80 
COMMAND  PID  USER   FD   TYPE DEVICE SIZE/OFF NODE NAME
nginx   1954  root    6u  IPv4  25674      0t0  TCP *:http (LISTEN)
nginx   1955 nginx    6u  IPv4  25674      0t0  TCP *:http (LISTEN)

#kill -9 1954
#kill -9 1955



2) Start docker-compose again:

# docker-compose start
Starting app ... done
Starting data ... done
Starting mysql ... done
Starting php ... done
Starting nginx ... done
Starting phpmyadmin ... done


No errors! Success! :)
